<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_05_IH_0006</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_05.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0006 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="6_deep_green" class="is_star" lang="y">
					비례식에서 내항의 곱이 84일 때 ㉠과 ㉡에 알맞은 수의 합을 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 lang="y">㉠과 ㉡에 알맞은 수를 각각 구해 보세요.</h3>
					<div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_05_IH/0006_bg.png" alt="" />
							<p>7 : 3=㉠ : ㉡</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<div class="flex align_center gap_10">
								<i class="num_sign">ㄱ</i>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="28"></math-field>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex align_center gap_10">
								<i class="num_sign">ㄴ</i>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p>내항의 곱이 84이므로 3×㉠=84, ㉠=28입니다.</p>
									<p>외항의 곱은 내항의 곱과 같으므로 7×㉡= 84, ㉡=12입니다.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 lang="y">㉠과 ㉡에 알맞은 수의 합을 구해 보세요.</h3>
					<div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_05_IH/0006_bg.png" alt="" />
							<p>7 : 3=㉠ : ㉡</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_wrap">
							<math-field data-answer-single="40"></math-field>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p>㉠=28, ㉡=12이므로</p>
									<p>㉠+㉡=28+12=40입니다.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div>
				</article>
			</section>
		</div>
		<script>
			runAfterAppReady(() => {
				$(".page_2 .btnSubmit").click(function () {
					$(".page_2 .solve_area").addClass("active");
				});
				$(".page_2 .btnReset").click(function () {
					$(".page_2 .solve_area").removeClass("active");
				});
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
